parameters.name: AcceptLanguage
parameters.description:
The language of the response. Valid values:

*   zh: Chinese
*   en: English

parameters.name: ClusterType
parameters.description: The type of the instance. Valid values: ZooKeeper, Nacos-Ans, and Eureka.

parameters.name: MseVersion
parameters.description:
The instance edition. Valid values:

*   `mse_dev`: Developer Edition.
*   `mse_pro`: Professional Edition. This is the default value.
